@startuml
title
<size:16><b>UC-05: Search and Filter Products - Activity Diagram</b></size>
end title

|Buyer|
start

:Type keyword in search bar and press Enter / click search icon;

|System|
if (Search bar empty?) then (yes)
  :Display all approved listings (status 'Approved', stock > 0) sorted by newest;
  note right: Alternative Flow 1
else (no)
  :Query product catalogue for approved listings matching keyword
   (title, description, brand, model - case insensitive);
endif

if (No matching results found?) then (yes)
  :Display 'No results for [keyword]' and suggest popular categories;
  note right: Alternative Flow 2
  stop
else (no)
endif

:Display results in product grid (thumbnail, title, price, condition, seller rating);

|Buyer|
:Apply filters (Category, Brand, Price Range, Condition, Seller Rating, Availability);

|System|
:Update results in real-time based on selected filters;

|Buyer|
:Sort results (Relevance, Price Low/High, Newest, Seller Rating);

|System|
:Display updated sorted results;

|Buyer|
:Select a product to view its detail page;

stop
@enduml